name: Target
directions: Family restroom is on the right just before you get to the two gendered restrooms.
comment:
Family restroom is a locking single stall gender nonspecific, wheelchair accessible restroom with a changing table.

Gendered restrooms can be used as befitting your gender identity — Target corporate policy requires them to have your back on this if any unsavories try to make your experience unpleasant.
